The paper deals with the structural properties of independent sets in graphs, which is a topic in discrete mathematics (cs.DM). It also involves the study of critical independent sets, which is related to graph theory (cs.GT) and computational geometry (cs.CG). The paper presents algorithms and computational results, which falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
